Add verified activity spots, historical analysis, and activity-filtered location selector

- Add verified kiting spots: Rush Lake, Grantsville Reservoir (Utah Windriders confirmed)
- Add paragliding sites: PotM South/North, Inspiration Point, West Mountain, Stockton Bar (UHGPGA verified)
- Add snowkite terrain: Powder Mountain, Monte Cristo (Utah Kite Addiction verified)
- LakeSelector now filters by activity: kiting sees kite spots, paragliding sees launch sites, fishing/boating sees lakes
- Historical spot analysis script pulls 365 days of Synoptic data for all verified spots
- Zig Zag confirmed: 198 SE thermal days/year, 340 total kiteable days from FPS station data
- Historical baseline data saved to src/config/historicalSpotData.json for prediction calibration
- Server cron expanded to collect data for all new activity-specific locations
